sql:
SELECT user_name
FROM users
WHERE user_id IN (
  SELECT DISTINCT user_id
  FROM training_sessions
);

external_knowledge:
- Concluded session refers to sessions where ts.status = 'completed'; 
- 'CartPole-v1' world refers to ts.environment = 1. 
- Average reward refers to AVG(cs.ep_rew_mean); 
- Average success rate refers to AVG(cs.success_rate).

sql:
SELECT session_id, status
   FROM training_sessions
   WHERE user_id = (SELECT user_id FROM users WHERE user_name = 'Alice Johnson');
